text.tspan: Become a SRCF member: free for life https://www.srcf.ucam.org/signup/
We exist as a university society to provide useful, flexible computing and network services
for University of Cambridge Staff and Students of all degrees of ability.
* Website hosting with a rich variety of features
* 500MB of file or webspace (and more if required)
* Free lifelong email and website forwarding when you graduate
* All of the above for any society you want the SRCF to host as well
* And much much more - see www.srcf.ucam.org/services/ for more details
